61 Vende la carne loro essendo viva;
62 poscia li ancide come antica belva;
63 molti di vita e sé di pregio priva.

query.result:
**English:**

61 He sells their flesh while they are still alive;
62 then he kills them like a savage beast;
63 he deprives many of life and themselves of dignity.

**Old English:**

61 He sellað heora flæsc ða ða hit cwic bið;
62 siððan he hit ofslihð swa sum unlæde wilddeor;
63 manega he ðæs lifes and ðæs wurðmyntes benimað.

